Steps to implement Docker (short & clear)
️⃣ Create Dockerfile (no extension)
Paste:
FROM nginx:alpine
COPY . /usr/share/nginx/html

️⃣ Open terminal in project folder
(Make sure Docker Desktop is running)

️⃣ Build Docker image
docker build -t bio-data-app .

️⃣ Verify image created
docker images
 OR check in Docker Desktop → Images tab

️⃣ (Optional) Run container
docker run -d -p 8080:80 bio-data-app
docker ps - gives all the detiials of the images created

